## 🚀 Philosophy

> “Security is not about assumptions — it is about continuous validation.”

Most breaches occur not due to lack of security tools, but due to:
- Unseen misconfigurations  
- Unpatched endpoints  
- Exposed services  
- Lack of real-world testing  

My objective is to expose these risks **before adversaries do**.

